      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Establishes a Civic Education Grant Program to provide support to public middle and intermediate schools in providing civic education to students through department approved programming. Establishes a Civic Education Trust Fund.  Effective 7/1/3000.  (HD1)"
    }
